    public abstract class GUITemplate
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This is week 1 stuff for CSCI 4997. Previously Named AtiburcioTyler_Week1 This abstract class provides a basic foundation and function for a java GUI (JPanel) application Comes with a status bar CHANGELOG: Changed extended class from JFrame to JPanel

    0.5
    Author:
    Tyler Atiburcio
